definitions.definition: An independent city in North Rhine-Westphalia , Germany , on the Rhine River; the former capital of West Germany and (until 1999) seat of government of unified Germany .

main_definition: An independent city in North Rhine-Westphalia , Germany , on the Rhine River; the former capital of West Germany and (until 1999) seat of government of unified Germany .
secondary_definitions: ( metonymic , historical after 1999 ) The (West) German government .
